#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:1
msgid "Environment variables"
msgstr "環境變數"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:3
msgid ""
"All configuration values can be overridden from the command line by setting "
"the corresponding environment variable. Because many operating systems "
"restrict environment variables to be alphanumeric characters or `_`, the "
"configuration key needs to be formatted slightly differently to the normal "
"`foo.bar.baz` form."
msgstr ""
"所有組態值都可以從命令行透過設定對應的環境變數來覆蓋。由於許多作業系統限制環"
"境變數僅能包含英數字元或底線（`_`），因此需將組態鍵稍微格式化為不同於普通的 "
"`foo.bar.baz` 形式。"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:8
msgid ""
"Variables starting with `MDBOOK_` are used for configuration. The key is "
"created by removing the `MDBOOK_` prefix and turning the resulting string "
"into `kebab-case`. Double underscores (`__`) separate nested keys, while a "
"single underscore (`_`) is replaced with a dash (`-`)."
msgstr ""
"使用以 `MDBOOK_` 開頭的變數進行組態。鍵（key）的建立方式是移除 `MDBOOK_` 前"
"綴，並將剩餘的字串轉換為 `kebab-case`。雙底線（`__`）用於分隔嵌套的鍵，而單底"
"線（`_`）則會被替換為短橫線 (`-`)。"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:13
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "例如："

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:15
msgid "`MDBOOK_book` -> `book`"
msgstr "`MDBOOK_book` -> `book`"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:16
msgid "`MDBOOK_BOOK` -> `book`"
msgstr "`MDBOOK_BOOK` -> `book`"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:17
msgid "`MDBOOK_BOOK__TITLE` -> `book.title`"
msgstr "`MDBOOK_BOOK__TITLE` -> `book.title`"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:18
msgid "`MDBOOK_BOOK__TEXT_DIRECTION` -> `book.text-direction`"
msgstr "`MDBOOK_BOOK__TEXT_DIRECTION` -> `book.text-direction`"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:20
msgid ""
"So by setting the `MDBOOK_BOOK__TITLE` environment variable you can override "
"the book's title without needing to touch your `book.toml`."
msgstr ""
"因此，透過設定 `MDBOOK_BOOK__TITLE` 環境變數而無需修改您的 `book.toml`，就可"
"以覆蓋手冊的題名。"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:23
msgid ""
"**Note:** To facilitate setting more complex config items, the value of an "
"environment variable is first parsed as JSON, falling back to a string if "
"the parse fails."
msgstr ""

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:27
msgid ""
"This means, if you so desired, you could override all book metadata when "
"building the book with something like"
msgstr ""
"這代表如果您有需要，可以在建置手冊時透過類似以下的方式覆蓋所有手冊的元資料"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:30
msgid ""
"```shell\n"
"$ export MDBOOK_BOOK='{\"title\": \"My Awesome Book\", \"authors\": "
"[\"Michael-F-Bryan\"]}'\n"
"$ mdbook build\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```shell\n"
"$ export MDBOOK_BOOK='{\"title\": \"My Awesome Book\", \"authors\": "
"[\"Michael-F-Bryan\"]}'\n"
"$ mdbook build\n"
"```"

#: src/format/configuration/environment-variables.md:35
msgid ""
"The latter case may be useful in situations where `mdbook` is invoked from a "
"script or CI, where it sometimes isn't possible to update the `book.toml` "
"before building."
msgstr ""
